/PATCHSET_LEVEL.message:
There is an issue with the host property show command. It joins property values with a new line even when using json output:

$ openstack reservation host property show foo -f json 2>/dev/null
{
  "private": false,
  "property": "foo",
  "property_values": "bar\nbuzz"
}

However the `list --detail` command works as expected:

$ openstack reservation host property list --detail -f json 2>/dev/null
[
  {
    "property": "foo",
    "private": false,
    "property_values": [
      "bar",
      "buzz"
    ]
  }
]

